## The situation

Bramblewood Dental has three providers — a general dentist, an orthodontist, and a hygienist — serving families across Greenville. They've built their patient base through referrals and a solid reputation. The clinical work is excellent.

But the front desk was drowning in phone calls, and new patients were slipping through the cracks.

## The problems

- **No online booking**: New patients had to call during 8am-5pm hours to schedule. Most people search for dentists in the evening
- **Phone bottleneck**: Front desk spent 30% of their time answering the same questions — "Do you take my insurance?" "What does a cleaning cost?" "Are you accepting new patients?"
- **No provider profiles**: Patients couldn't learn about their dentist before the first visit
- **Competitors booking online**: Other practices with online scheduling captured the patients who searched after hours

## What we built

### Online booking

Two clear paths: "New Patient" and "Existing Patient." New patients see what to expect at their first visit and can book directly. Existing patients pick their provider and schedule in seconds.

### Team profiles

Each provider gets a profile — photo, credentials, specialties, and a personal note. Patients choosing a dentist want to know who'll be working on them. This builds trust before the first appointment.

### Insurance and payment page

A clear list of accepted insurance plans, payment options, and financing information. This is the #1 question new patients ask — putting it on the site saves the front desk hundreds of calls.

### AI assistant

The chat answers patient questions 24/7: "Do you do Invisalign?" "What's a crown procedure like?" "Are you open on Saturdays?" It knows the full service list, provider schedules, and insurance information.

### New patient onboarding

A "New Patient? Start Here" section walks first-time visitors through what to expect — forms to fill out online, what to bring, parking info, and a direct booking link.

## The results

- **After-hours booking**: New patients scheduling at 9pm instead of going to a competitor
- **Front desk relief**: AI handles repetitive questions, staff focuses on in-office patients
- **Provider trust**: Patients feel comfortable before their first visit
- **Google visibility**: Showing up for "dentist Greenville SC" and "family dentist near me"

Visit the site: [demo-medical.pages.dev](https://demo-medical.pages.dev)

## Why this matters for your business

If you run a dental practice, medical office, or any healthcare business — your patients are searching for you after hours. If they can't book online or get their questions answered, they'll book with the practice that can. A modern site with booking and an AI assistant means your practice grows while you sleep.

